1
00:01:02,119 --> 00:01:02,759
Put her down.

2
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,759
Your Highness,

3
00:01:05,119 --> 00:01:06,920
you must be very busy.

4
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,159
But you still have time to deal with this.

5
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,519
If you don't want to die,

6
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,480
put her down.

7
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:14,040
Your Highness, what's your identity?

8
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,079
Please don't hurt him.

9
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,159
Boss Bai.

10
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,400
Put me down.

11
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,120
Thank you for saving my life.

12
00:01:38,599 --> 00:01:39,239
I will

13
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:41,640
I'll repay you for saving me.

14
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,599
Master,

15
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,759
that girl from the Nuo Opera Troupe

16
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,960
was rescued by someone.

17
00:02:59,159 --> 00:03:00,000
Who?

18
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,800
Bai Weiran, the owner of the bank.

19
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,719
I'll find out who he is.

20
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,639
Also,

21
00:03:04,639 --> 00:03:06,159
Prince Xian...

22
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,800
What happened?

23
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:10,759
You asked me to release those two snake demons

24
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,400
to stall him from saving that girl.

25
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:15,159
But Your Highness used blood to awaken

26
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,439
the Soul-Devouring Bone Sword.

27
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,319
Its power surged,

28
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:20,360
and the snakes were slain instantly.

29
00:03:20,879 --> 00:03:23,280
He's truly gone too far.

30
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:26,039
The bracelet didn't hold her?

31
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,400
I checked the Vice Minister's Mansion.

32
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,719
The bracelet is broken.

33
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:32,439
Only a dream demon could've

34
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:33,759
broken it herself.

35
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:37,800
Has His Highness the Virtuous Prince continued investigating the ghost marriage?

36
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,280
When he arrived,

37
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,000
the girl was rescued by Bai Weiran.

38
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,800
He's been searching for her,

39
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:45,400
but hasn't found out about the bracelet.

40
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,159
Nor has he dug into the snake demon case.

41
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:49,960
Take care of everyone

42
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:51,400
and everything

43
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,520
related to this.

44
00:03:53,520 --> 00:03:54,080
Yes.

45
00:04:04,719 --> 00:04:05,560
[Li,]

46
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,800
[I've been by your side for a century,]

47
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:11,080
[loving you for a century.]

48
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,199
[Why did you choose him in both lives?]

49
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,680
Regaining the Spiritual Root,

50
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,439
gaining trust,

51
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:25,199
are these just excuses?

52
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,040
Heaven...

53
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,680
Any more?

54
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:54,759
This is the last one.

55
00:05:01,519 --> 00:05:02,319
Are you a demon

56
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,720
or a human?

57
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,920
Such a strong demon aura.

58
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:19,040
What kind of demon are you?

59
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:20,240
I don't know

60
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,920
either.

61
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,560
I cultivate by consuming nightmares.

62
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,720
I have no true form.

63
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:29,800
Little butterfly,

64
00:05:30,399 --> 00:05:32,079
if you don't want to be bullied,

65
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:33,800
you have to become strong on your own.

66
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,519
Just wait.

67
00:05:44,199 --> 00:05:45,040
When I get stronger,

68
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,160
I will repay you.

69
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,319
Then why not repay me now?

70
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,800
Help me find the nightmare seed,

71
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,600
and I'll protect you.

72
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,480
How does that sound?

73
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:55,399
Okay.

74
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,199
Where are you hurt?

75
00:06:27,959 --> 00:06:28,759
Boss Bai

76
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,759
has already treated my wound.

77
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,519
You watched me

78
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,879
being close to that stranger,

79
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:51,160
but you can't do the same with me?

80
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:05,319
Let go of me!

81
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:12,160
What did I do wrong?

82
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,279
Why do you all treat me with such disdain?

83
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:17,279
Why is it always me?

84
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:22,519
Why do I have to suffer such humiliation?

85
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:25,160
Just because I'm lowborn?

86
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,639
You rich

87
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,680
and privileged,

88
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,680
do you have to trample on others' values?

89
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:37,560
I'm an orphan from the Nuo Opera Troupe.

90
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,680
So I don't deserve respect

91
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,800
or genuine affection?

92
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:54,560
It's not your fault.

93
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,639
It's mine.

94
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:28,480
Isn't this

95
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:30,720
what you wanted?

96
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:34,279
I...

97
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,879
What's wrong?

98
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,240
Or do you think

99
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,039
I'm only good enough

100
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,559
to win over the Minister?

101
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:49,799
I never meant that.

102
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,960
I'm sorry I was late

103
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,519
and made you suffer all this.

104
00:08:55,559 --> 00:08:56,559
It's my fault.

105
00:08:58,720 --> 00:09:00,759
Didn't you deliberately send me away?

106
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:02,279
I can't even protect you.

107
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,159
How could I do such a heartless thing?

108
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,159
I thought

109
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:24,120
you hate me

110
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:27,480
and never want to see me again.

111
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,960
I don't hate you.

112
00:09:30,519 --> 00:09:31,960
I just want to protect you.

113
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,080
Are you serious?

114
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:42,759
If you don't believe me,

115
00:09:44,279 --> 00:09:44,840
I can...

116
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,399
I believe you.

117
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:19,960
[This time,]

118
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,200
[I didn't come late.]

119
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,919
[It's too late to make up]

120
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,639
[in a dream.]

121
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,360
[Finally, it's open.]

122
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,799
[As long as he cares for me]

123
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,799
[and feels genuine emotions,]

124
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:41,440
[I can enter the deeper dream.]

125
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,720
I've heard that

126
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,720
when a demon reaches adulthood,

127
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,399
a demon hairpin will grow.

128
00:11:24,799 --> 00:11:26,240
Why is the mark on your forehead

129
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:27,480
so faint?

130
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:33,080
A demon hairpin

131
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,960
needs Spirit-Guiding Sand to awaken.

132
00:11:35,679 --> 00:11:36,919
Once awakened,

133
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,600
it signifies the awakening of your demon nature,

134
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:39,600
and a surge in your demon power.

135
00:11:40,679 --> 00:11:41,480
But

136
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,320
I have no demon kin.

137
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,519
That's why

138
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:47,240
my hairpin remains dim.

139
00:11:47,799 --> 00:11:49,320
Only a demon kin can ignite it?

140
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,399
If you find your true love,

141
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:01,159
your husband can also ignite it.

142
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,200
Who are you talking about?

143
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,120
Your husband.

144
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:24,360
[His deep dreams]

145
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:27,759
[is our past life.]

146
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,159
[The past]

147
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:33,799
[is just a dream to you.]

148
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,559
Daozhi,

149
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:42,080
what do you

150
00:12:42,399 --> 00:12:43,399
need from me?

151
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:46,200
Li,

152
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:49,559
I need to tell you something important.

153
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,600
What is it?

154
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,000
Before I met you,

155
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:55,000
my world was small.

156
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,039
Hunting demons,

157
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:58,440
[and cultivation]

158
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:00,200
[were dull,]

159
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:02,159
[predictable.]

160
00:13:03,919 --> 00:13:05,159
[But since I met you,]

161
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:07,519
[I've found that a day]

162
00:13:08,000 --> 00:13:09,559
[can be so fleeting.]

163
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:11,960
[Every moment with you,]

164
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:14,320
[my heart leaps with joy.]

165
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,320
[It turns out]

166
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,720
[that having someone to miss]

167
00:13:18,639 --> 00:13:20,360
[makes every day worth looking forward to.]

168
00:13:23,799 --> 00:13:24,879
[A'Li,]

169
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:29,799
I've admired you for a long time.

170
00:13:31,399 --> 00:13:32,600
From now on,

171
00:13:33,759 --> 00:13:35,159
will you stay by my side?

172
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,399
I...

173
00:13:48,200 --> 00:13:49,039
I'm a demon.

174
00:13:50,799 --> 00:13:52,000
And you're a demon hunter.

175
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,240
I don't care if you're a demon.

176
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,000
I only care

177
00:13:56,639 --> 00:13:58,519
if you're willing to be with me forever.

178
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,399
Every year,

179
00:14:21,919 --> 00:14:23,480
I'll light the demon hairpin for you.

180
00:14:24,879 --> 00:14:26,360
I'll be your closest and dearest.

181
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,240
Will you?

182
00:14:56,799 --> 00:14:57,519
A'Li,

183
00:14:59,799 --> 00:15:01,000
I, Shen Daozhi,

184
00:15:01,399 --> 00:15:02,720
swear to love you forever.

185
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,919
If I ever break this oath,

186
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,720
may I die and lose my cultivation.

187
00:15:10,759 --> 00:15:12,039
[A traitor...]

188
00:15:12,879 --> 00:15:14,159
[A traitor]

189
00:15:15,159 --> 00:15:16,840
[doesn't deserve to remember any of this.]
